{"tid":2328661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平安夜記念活動","createTime":"2020-12-16T16:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T06:41:51.000Z","uid":374427,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa57729182f5aae021012d9a1b809ed8fd1958f","tid":2328661,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T16:25:27.000Z","msg":"承上post<br />\n<br />\n平安夜活動!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2318766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2318766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n而家出左活動地方，請大家幫忙推推<br />\n<br />\n推比多人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想去到最後冇人、迫於無奈減地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5AeHPXk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5AeHPXk.jpg&h=3bb5ec56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020年12月24日 (平安夜) 8:00pm<br />\n對象：仍在香港又未放棄嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n記念今個聖誕無法團圓嘅每一個家庭<br />\n(包括：武肺死者家人，已逝/在囚/還押中/流亡手足及其家庭)<br />\n毋忘12位被送中港人<br />\n<br />\n留意：<br />\n1) 疫情原因，請大家做好預防疾病傳染措施<br />\n  (例如：帶口罩，企疏D...)<br />\n2) 599G仍然生效，請大家保持安全距離<br />\n3) 相信警方當日會投放大量警力於各區&ldquo;維持秩序&ldquo;，大家小心<br />\n4) 是次目的為記念無法團圓的家庭，不建議有暴力場面，亦盡量避免衝突發生<br />\n<br />\n入黎telegram以獲得最新資訊<br />\nTG Channel Link:<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/SilentCandleNight\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSilentCandleNight&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE17M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=1ae19c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/SilentCandleNight</a><br />\n<br />\n同時Fb都有Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101691561822494/posts/101693658488951/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101691561822494%2Fposts%2F101693658488951%2F&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE17M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2B